OL,3,CFormer Coronation Street actor dies of
OL,4,Cheart attack at 72
OL,6,FFormer Coronation Street John Saint
OL,7,FRyan has died suddenly, aged 72, after
OL,8,Fsuffering a heart attack.
OL,10,FThe actor, who was known for playing
OL,11,Florry driver Charlie Whelan in the
OL,12,Fsoap between 1993 to 1994, died on
OL,13,FThursday, 3 April, surrounding by his
OL,14,Ffamily, his wife Joyce said.
OL,16,FIn a post on Facebook, his Joyce
OL,17,Fwrote: "I and our family want to let
OL,18,Four friends know that John had a heart
OL,19,Fattack the evening of Thursday 3rd of
OL,20,FApril.
