OL,6,F"We were with him at the hospital
OL,7,Fwhere the staff did everything
OL,8,Fpossible but unfortunately he did not
OL,9,Fsurvive.
OL,11,F"We are absolutely heart broken. John
OL,12,Fwanted to aid medical research and
OL,13,Fdonated his body, so there will not be
OL,14,Fa funeral. Later, we will arrange a
OL,15,Fcelebration of his wonderful life.
OL,17,F"We are all fortunate to have known
OL,18,Fand loved this special 'Gentleman' as
OL,19,Fhe has been described to me numerous
OL,20,Ftimes over the last couple of days."
