OL,6,FJohn was born in Burnley, Lancashire
OL,7,Fin 1953 and spent most of his earlier
OL,8,Flife in the world of Martial Arts,
OL,9,Fboth as a fighter and a teacher before
OL,10,Fhe became an actor.
OL,12,FAs long-distance lorry driver Charlie
OL,13,FWhelan in Corrie, he began a
OL,14,Frelationship with Rovers Return
OL,15,Flandlady Bet Gilroy, played by Julie
OL,16,FGoodyear, during her separation from
OL,17,Fhusband Alec Gilroy, played by Roy
OL,18,FBarraclough.
