OL,6,FAfter his 10-month stint on the show,
OL,7,Fthe actor then moved to California
OL,8,Fwhere he landed various supporting
OL,9,Froles including in the hit series
OL,10,FBuffy the Vampire Slayer, Murder She
OL,11,FWrote and The Heidi Chronicles.
OL,13,FJohn, a horse trainer and equestrian,
OL,14,Falso owned his own ranch in Inyokern
OL,15,FCalifornia, were he raised boarded and
OL,16,Fsold horses.
